<h3 id="capo-1st-fret-standard-tuning">Capo 1st Fret, Standard Tuning</h3>
<p>To play this song along with the Johnny Cash album recording, put a capo on the 1st fret. If playing along doesnâ€™t matter to you, you can play it without a capo (using the chords shown here) just fine.</p>

<h3 id="guitar-chords-used">Guitar Chords Used</h3>
<p>Here are the chords youâ€™ll need to play this song. These are all quite common open chords, with the B7 being the most rare of the bunch. Donâ€™t let the B7 scare you off! It is a useful chord to have in your repertoire.</p>

