<h3 id="transition-between-verses">Transition Between Verses</h3>
<p>Here are the tabs for the transition between each verse, where the song in fact changes key. After you walk up/down to the new chord, stay on that chord as long as you like. This is where Johnny Cash will do the â€œHmmmmmmâ€¦â€ vocal, which helps establish the new key in which he is about to play.</p>

